Hi,

Thanks for expressing interest in our group!

To subscribe send an email to glb-knit-subscribe@groups.queernet.org from the address you wish to subscribe with the text:

subscribe glb-knit [your email address] [your name] 

in the body of the email. And that's it. The system should generate an email that I have to approve, and baring natural disaster I should be able be able to process that within a day or so. You'll get confirmation of this by email soon. Remember to introduce yourself to the group, we're quite friendly.

Cheers,
